column1: Engage magnet
Pickup tips from A column 11
Move to Reagent Cartridge tray A column 5 with 50 uL tips
Aspirate 12 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Move to Pre-Amp Thermocycler column 1 with 50 uL tips moving up by 30000
Dispense 11 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Delay for 3 seconds
Dispense 5 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Move to Mag Separator column 3 with 50 uL tips moving up by 4000
Aspirate 15 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Move to Pre-Amp Thermocycler column 1 with 50 uL tips moving up by 30000
Dispense 15 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Move relative down by 30000
Mix 20 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 3 times
Delay for 2 seconds
Dispense 5 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Eject tips in A column 11
Pickup tips from A column 5
Move to Reagent Cartridge tray A column 7 with 50 uL tips
Aspirate 27 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Delay for 5 seconds
Move to Pre-Amp Thermocycler column 1 with 50 uL tips moving up by 30000
Dispense 27 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Delay for 5 seconds
Dispense 10 uLs with 50 uL tips at Low pressure 1 time
Eject tips in A column 5
Thermocycle Pre-Amp at 95 C for 3 minutes and cycle 6 times between 95 C for 120 seconds and 60 C for 240 seconds
